column5: Hey guys, gonna make this one short as im pretty exhausted from sleepin 3 hours a night. Decided to get out with a bud on simcoe today, for the 3d time this year, been too busy with other lakes to get out there, despite simcoe being almost my backyard. Was nice to sleep in and still hammer a bunch if whities!
Holy cow. Everyone was on the money today!
Thanks guys, simcoe has been insane every trip out this season, my buds hammered them on simcoe yesterday but so did i up north
Did the Whitey season just open this weekend??????You would think so, lol,Good going !!!!!
Something was in the air on sunday in ontario...everyone seems to have absolutely killed it!
Saturday was even better i heard on simcoe, maybe there will have a few more good bites on simcoe before the ice comes off completely..,
